<span class="headers">Coldain Insignia Ring Quests </span>
<p>
<h4>(<i>Tradeskill portion only</i>)</h4> 
<p>
This is only the tradeskill portion of the first and third coldain insignia rings. For a complete write-up on the quest, please see the <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/quest/garadainsrings.html" target="_new">Garadain's Rings writeup</a> on EQ'Lizer
</p> 
<p>
Ring 1: <b>Copper Coldain Insignia Ring</b>: +1 AC, +1 Str, +1 Save vs Magic, All/All
</p>
<p>
Garadain Glacierbane, a dwarf in the huts northeast of the Ry'gorr fort, is looking for a blanket to keep him warm. In return for this blanket you receive the Copper Coldain Ring. The blanket is made by combining 4 pelts in a tailoring kit:
</p>
<table border="1">
<tr><th>Item</th><th>Recipe</th><th>Trivial</th></tr>
<tr>
<td class="intable"><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5293&menustr=">Coldain Hunting Blanket</a></td><td class="intable">Components: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1357">high quality cougarskin</a>(2), <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1359">high quality tundra kodiak pelt</a>(2)<br />In: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1427">small sewing kit</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1614">deluxe sewing kit</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1733">large sewing kit</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1791">loom</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5228">planar sewing kit</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7340">collapsible sewing kit</a><br />Notes: Previously reported Trivial 41. Another report of Trivial at 44. Definitely Conflicting Information.</td><td align="center" class="intable">82</td>
</tr>
</table>

<p>
Tundra Kodiaks in the Eastern Wastes drop the High Quality Tundra Kodiak Pelts. Snow Cougars in the Eastern Wastes and Iceclad Ocean drop the High Quality Snow Cougar Pelts.
</p> 
<p>
Ring 3: <b>Gold Coldain Insignia Ring</b>: +3 AC, +3 Str, +3 Save vs Magic, All/All
</p>
<p>
Garadain Glacierbane, a dwarf in the huts northeast of the Ry'gorr fort, is looking for a hunting knife. This is made by combining a Skinning Rock, a High Quality Walrus Hide, and a Wooly Rhino Horn in a forge. This produces a nodrop Hunting Knife. This is trivial at a smithing skill of 41.
</p> 
<p>
Walruses in the Eastern Wastes drop the High Quality Walrus Hides. Wooly Rhinos in the Eastern Wastes drop the Wooly Rhino Horn. Skinning rocks are found in the Eastern Wastes as ground spawns, they look like a rough black rock on the ground and an egg shape in inventory. Skinning rocks are no drop
</p>
<p>
Ring 9: <b>Coldain Hero's Insignia Ring</b>: +9 AC, +9 Str, +9 Sta, +9 Save vs Magic, +50 HP, Effect: Shield of the Eighth (Right-clickable and stackable 8 point damage shield)
</p>
<p>
Need to make <i>Tainted Avalance Ale</i>
</p>
<p>
(Making this recipe is only step 3 of several steps to acquire this ring). <i>Write-up to come</i>
</p>
<ol>
<li> <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=7098&menustr=">Quicksilver</a> = Components: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7140">cinnabar</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=4176">gnomish spirits</a><br />In: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1745">mortar and pestle</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7339">collapsible mortar and pestle</a> </li>
<li> <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=1625&menustr=">Sealed Poison Vial</a> = Components: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1333">high quality firing sheet</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=3943">unfired sealed poison vial</a><br />In: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1751">kiln</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5496">tanaan kiln</a> </li>
<li> <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5224&menustr=">Mind Melt</a> = Components: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7024">ethereal suspension</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5254">mt. death mineral salts</a>(2), <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7098">quicksilver</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1625">sealed poison vial</a><br />In: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1745">mortar and pestle</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7131">marble mortar and pestle</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=7339">collapsible mortar and pestle</a><br />On Failure Returns: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1625">sealed poison vial</a><br />This combine may only be made by Rogues
 </li>
<li> <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=5218&menustr=">Tainted Avalanche Ale</a> = Components: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5221">arctic mussels</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1285">bottle</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5220">ice wyvern stinger</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5219">iceball</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5224">mind melt</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5223">runed sea shell</a>, <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=5222">seahorse scales</a><br />In: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1457">brew barrel</a><br />On Failure Returns: <a href="/items/show_item.php?item=1285">bottle</a><br />Notes: Coldain Ring Quest #9<br/>
Be sure to use the Runed Sea Shell with the Cloud effect. </li>
</ol>
</p><p>
